name: Ace of Wands
description:
Cryp-tarot - 001

Meaning - Inspiration, new opportunities, growth, potential

The Ace of Wands encourages you to follow your heart and live your passions. Let your energy, dedication and motivation be your guiding light. Keep in mind, however, that the Aces represent potential and not guaranteed results. The Ace of Wands may appear when you have an opportunity to grow on a personal or spiritual level. Trust that this experience will open you up to even more possibilities.
